name: Parkour (itch) (TheOneWhoWill)
description:
This is a First Person Platformer set in outer space. This project was built for Peanut Jam hosted by Techcodes.  It has custom graphics settings, and is integrated with Discord.

When opening the game change the graphics settings otherwise it will default to low settings. It is built for Windows and I'm too lazy to port over to anything else.

Credits go to:

  1.  Muhammad Rafikov
  2. Xinpeng Gao
